data.description:
WOW! New Price, motivated seller! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 2-car garage, ideally located near the lake and boat ramp. The home boasts a modern farmhouse feel with lovely Pergo barnwood wood Waterproof flooring and a cozy wood-burning fireplace in the living area. The kitchen features granite countertops, a subway tile backsplash, an island, and new appliances. The master bedroom leads to a spacious master bathroom with walk-in closets and an impressive walk-in tile shower with a stone base. Two additional bedrooms share a bathroom with granite countertops, and there's a versatile bonus space, perfect for a home office, 4th bedroom, guest accommodations, or a bunk room for an AirBnB. 

This home is situated in the Rolling Oaks community, known for its sandy beaches along Lake Eufaula, offering beach and ramp access just a block away. Outdoor living is easy with two patios, one of which is covered, and a fully fenced backyard bordering wooded land. This property has great rental potential, boasts a sandy beach at your doorstep, and is conveniently located just North of Eufaula. It can be purchased fully furnished for a seamless transition. With its ideal location, this lakeside retreat is within reach of Oklahoma City, Tulsa, and Dallas. Don't miss your chance—Seller is motivated, call today for a private tour and start your lakeside adventure today.
